commitResults.messageBody: Remove short command version for consistency with other commands

Here are the areas of improvement detected:
- The Ui.png image of ToothTracker needs to be updated.
- There were inconsistencies in `list` command formats. Only singular commands will be used.
- The placement of "Format:" for command formats were also inconsistent. They are placed after the first paragraph of a command.
- There were errors in documenting optional input commands with square brackets. These have been corrected.
- There were attributes that were in lower-case. They should have been in UPPER_CASE.
- There were missing commands for `filter-appointment`. These have been corrected.
- Command Summary was not updated

These have been standardized as of 25 Oct 2023 10:30pm.
